{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1016_00_01","textHome":"唔，想尽量了解和我相关的事情，就这些。@嗯？还不行吗。这样啊……@没有爱好，喜欢的词汇是公平和平等。@虽然不容易看出来，但想当一个温柔的姐姐。@还有，以前划分在东边这一带，@和七海、梓有过激烈的竞争。差不多就这样。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101600}]}],"group_10":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1016_00_18","textHome":"拍照吗？我也能挣到钱，当然可以。@不过市里认识我的人有点多，@抱歉还是让我遮一下脸吧。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":200}]}],"group_11":[{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1016_00_19","textHome":"又获得了一种能用来实现公平的力量了。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":101600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":101600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.2,"chara":[{"id":101600}]}],"group_12":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.9,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1016_00_20","textHome":"唔，脱胎换骨的感觉。@回去的路上逮个魔女试试。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":101600,"motion":200}]}],"group_13":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1016_00_21","textHome":"做了魔法少女，位于人上的事情就多起来了。@别人来寻求帮助这一点，倒也不坏。@毕竟能够在狩猎魔女以外的事情上帮到别人。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.4,"chara":[{"id":101600,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":100}]}],"group_14":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1016_00_22","textHome":"魔法少女在共同的宿命之上是平等的。@无论生于何方，成为魔法少女的瞬间，@就背负了同样的重担。我会为成长而喜悦，@也是为了守护那样的同胞们。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":9.0,"chara":[{"id":101600,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":200}]}],"group_15":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1016_00_23","textHome":"毁灭神滨，是我对故乡最大的爱。@但是，没有能实现的办法。@所以第二层的爱，就是最大限度地守护它。@为此我要变强。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":101600,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":200}]}],"group_16":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1016_00_24","textHome":"嗨，主人难得光临！@唔，招呼有进步了吗。真是抱歉，@还是经常要你陪我做女仆咖啡厅接客的练习。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":8.3,"chara":[{"id":101600,"motion":300}]}],"group_17":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1016_00_25","textHome":"学着由比设计了早晨的体操，要看看吗？@晨间的十七夜体操开始。@首先伸直手臂，然后做摆臂运动！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.7,"chara":[{"id":101600,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.4,"chara":[{"id":101600,"motion":400}]}],"group_18":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1016_00_26","textHome":"唔，抱歉不能陪你去吃午饭。@其实我是自带了便当的。@用有限的食材做出各种花样很有意思。@试吃一个如何？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.2,"chara":[{"id":101600,"motion":100}]}],"group_19":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1016_00_27","textHome":"到这个时间，客人就多起来了，@偶尔也会收到作为礼物的点心。@那天家里的晚饭就有甜点吃了。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"id":101600,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":100}]}],"group_2":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1016_00_03","textHome":"我很少和他人这样说话，请你用心听。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":101600}]}],"group_20":[{"autoTurnFirst":7.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1016_00_28","textHome":"到了万籁俱寂的深夜，@就想起来八云成为魔法少女时的事情……@没想到我们的想法几乎一致……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.6,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":101600}]}],"group_21":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1016_00_29","textHome":"然而，由于魔女的增加，@魔法少女的社会变得和平了。@以前的领地问题已经绝迹，@现在成了没有边界的状态。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.7,"chara":[{"id":101600,"motion":100}]}],"group_22":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1016_00_30","textHome":"嗯，我知道你想说什么了。@是想一起去捕猎魔女吧？@稍等，店长打电话来了。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":0}]}],"group_23":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1016_00_31","textHome":"和镜之魔女已经共存很久了，@怎么也找不到结界里的魔女。@就算使用读心，@也完全没法理解使魔在说什么……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":101600,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":300}]}],"group_24":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1016_00_32","textHome":"这就是所谓的群雄割据吧。@虽然不喜欢魔法少女同伴之间的争斗，@但有明确理由的话也没办法。走吧。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.4,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":101600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":101600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":0}]}],"group_25":[{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1016_00_33","textHome":"无理、不义、不公，都是不共戴天的敌人。@如果有谁胆敢恣意妄为，无需多言，@我将予以制裁。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":101600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":101600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"id":101600,"motion":400}]}],"group_26":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1016_00_34","textHome":"喜欢自己出生的这片土地吗？我是很喜欢的。@从出生我就爱着这片土地，又在这里长大。@即便它有些乱，对我而言也是重要的地方。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":101600,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":101600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.9,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.2,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":101600}]}],"group_27":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1016_00_35","textHome":"嗯，糟糕了……@要上体育课的话，@一开始就穿着运动服来就好了。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":300}]}],"group_28":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1016_00_36","textHome":"现在我还能想起父亲在钢铁厂工作时的背影，@劳动者是很伟大的。@这也激励着我兼职时好好努力。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":200}]}],"group_29":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1016_00_37","textHome":"比较起月咲和月夜的时候，感觉很奇妙……@为什么她们双胞胎偏偏胸部有差距呢……@人体真是神秘啊。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.9,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.4,"chara":[{"id":101600,"motion":100}]}],"group_3":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1016_00_04","textHome":"我们至今都一直被过去绊住了脚步。"}]}],"group_30":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.9,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1016_00_38","textHome":"虽然跟七海她们有过很多次冲突，@但最终都是通过商谈化解了。@回想起来，大概我们的脾气是合得来的吧。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.3,"chara":[{"id":101600,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101600}]}],"group_31":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1016_00_39","textHome":"能让我稍微角色扮演一下吗？@傲娇、病娇、酷娇，@虽然听说过但还是不太了解……@为了学习就拜托你了。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":100}]}],"group_32":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1016_00_40","textHome":"名为历史的东西真碍事啊。@无论土地和人如何改变，@它就像亡灵一样将我们拖入过去的深渊。@真是令人感到空虚……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":9.3,"chara":[{"id":101600,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":101600,"motion":300}]}],"group_33":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1016_00_41","textHome":"呵，真是爱找人搭理。@再缠着我的话，就要仔细看看你的内心，@把你的秘密一点不剩地暴露出来哦？@好了，开玩笑的。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.7,"chara":[{"id":101600,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":200}]}],"group_34":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1016_00_42","textHome":"东边的调停者，登场！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"id":101600,"motion":400}]}],"group_35":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1016_00_43","textHome":"该说越发进步了吗？"}]}],"group_36":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1016_00_44","textHome":"店长打电话来了，得马上去店里！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":100}]}],"group_37":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1016_00_45","textHome":"生死是平等地给予我们的权利。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":100}]}],"group_38":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1016_00_46","textHome":"为自己的行动感到痛心，而后偿还吧。"}]}],"group_39":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1016_00_63","textHome":"如果想动手那就过来！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":101600}]}],"group_4":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1016_00_05","textHome":"虽然空虚，但也无可奈何……@因为这座城市里只有舍弃的理由……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"id":101600,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":101600}]}],"group_40":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.9,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1016_00_64","textHome":"别太直接，我已看穿一切！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.1,"chara":[{"id":101600,"motion":400}]}],"group_41":[{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1016_00_65","textHome":"抱歉，我将给予你们独一无二的平等！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.3,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":101600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":101600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":200}]}],"group_42":[{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1016_00_66","textHome":"生与死，你将去向何方？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.8,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":101600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":101600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.2,"chara":[{"id":101600,"motion":100}]}],"group_43":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1016_00_02","textHome":"想借助我和泉十七夜的力量的人，就是你吗？@但这句话是否真心，@就由我窥探你的内心来确定吧。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"id":101600,"motion":400}]}],"group_5":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1016_00_13","textHome":"唔，感觉不错。这就是鞭策出来的气势吧。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":101600,"motion":100}]}],"group_6":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.9,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1016_00_14","textHome":"以前就受八云的关照，现在更是如此了。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.9,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":200}]}],"group_7":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1016_00_15","textHome":"每句话都读一遍你的内心，这样也不介意吗？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.6,"chara":[{"id":101600,"motion":100}]}],"group_8":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1016_00_16","textHome":"变美味♪变美味♪这样真的会变好吃吗？@唔，把这个树桩蛋糕拿去给主人试试吧……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":101600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.7,"chara":[{"id":101600,"motion":100}]}],"group_9":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1016_00_17","textHome":"这样吗，想和女仆玩游戏啊。@那么就来扳手腕吧。@主人不多活动身体的话，会变迟钝的。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101600,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.7,"chara":[{"id":101600,"motion":100}]}]},"version":3}